define({"topics":[{"title":"Project management ","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">Even though the primary goal of a TMS is to automate a lot of tasks in the         translation process, it still requires <strong class=\"ph b\">people<\/strong> to manage it. <\/p>","href":"topics\/project_management.html","attributes":{"data-id":"project_management"},"menu":{"hasChildren":true},"tocID":"project_management-d571e183","next":"project_management-d571e183"},{"title":"Finance management ","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">The main reason for investing in a TMS is to reduce costs that your organization         spends on translation in general. See how can this tool help you achieve it.<\/p>","href":"topics\/finance_management.html","attributes":{"data-id":"finance_management"},"menu":{"hasChildren":true},"tocID":"finance_management-d571e297","next":"finance_management-d571e297"},{"title":"Content management","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">A TMS maintains all the translation-related content centrally to be accessed in real         time. <\/p>","href":"topics\/content_management.html","attributes":{"data-id":"content_management"},"menu":{"hasChildren":true},"tocID":"content_management-d571e330","next":"content_management-d571e330"},{"title":"Translation editor (Workbench)","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">Currently, hardly anyone translates in an original document, be it Word, HTML file or         InDesign. Most translators and reviewers work in <strong class=\"ph b\">special text editors<\/strong> that are core         CAT tool components.<\/p>","href":"topics\/translation_editor_workbench.html","attributes":{"data-id":"translation_editor_workbench"},"menu":{"hasChildren":true},"tocID":"translation_editor_workbench-d571e410","next":"translation_editor_workbench-d571e410"},{"title":"Quality management","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">There are still discussions on what should be considered a high-quality translation.         Is it an error-free document in the target language or the smooth process where every step         complies with the established procedure?<\/p>","href":"topics\/quality_management.html","attributes":{"data-id":"quality_management"},"menu":{"hasChildren":true},"tocID":"quality_management-d571e473","next":"quality_management-d571e473"},{"title":"Machine translation","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"glossary\/r_glossary.html#g_machine_translation\">Machine translation<\/a>         engines are third-party systems that are not standard components of a TMS. <\/p>","href":"topics\/machine_translation.html","attributes":{"data-id":"machine_translation"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"machine_translation-d571e508","topics":[]},{"title":"Connectors","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">Learn how to gain more control over your content by integrating content management         systems and translation management systems via a connector.<\/p>","href":"topics\/connectors.html","attributes":{"data-id":"connectors"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"connectors-d571e521","topics":[]},{"title":"Security","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">Nowadays, data security is on top of mind of all businesses, with the translation         industry being no exception. <\/p>","href":"topics\/security.html","attributes":{"data-id":"security"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"security-d571e532","topics":[]},{"title":"Documentation","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">When you start working with a new tool, it is extremely useful to have relevant         documentation at hand to refer to it when you need it. <\/p>","href":"topics\/documentation.html","attributes":{"data-id":"documentation"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"documentation-d571e543","topics":[]},{"title":"Support","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">High-quality documentation is useful, but in some cases it may not be enough. As with         every IT tool, with TMSs you can also experience technical problems. <\/p>","href":"topics\/support.html","attributes":{"data-id":"support"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"support-d571e554","topics":[]},{"title":"Product development","shortdesc":"<p class=\"shortdesc\">You have bought a TMS and what comes next? Since every IT tool is upgraded from time         to time and you get the new version instantly if you use the cloud-based software, you need         to be ready for constant changes.<\/p>","href":"topics\/product_development.html","attributes":{"data-id":"product_development"},"menu":{"hasChildren":false},"tocID":"product_development-d571e566","topics":[]}]});